00:00:10.050 --> 00:00:12.650
Nellie is a fearless and
passionate provocateur

00:00:12.650 --> 00:00:14.490
who was nominated
by "Icon" magazine

00:00:14.490 --> 00:00:17.900
as one of the 50 international
designers shaping the future.

00:00:17.900 --> 00:00:19.630
