magazine awarded

00:00:25.290 --> 00:00:28.390
Nellie with a "WIRED" Innovation
Fellowship for her work

00:00:28.390 --> 00:00:30.410
and its potential to
make a significant impact

00:00:30.410 --> 00:00:31.490
on the world.

00:00:31.490 --> 00:00:33.260
Her latest film,
"Disaster Playground,"

00:00:33.260 --> 00:00:34.760
has original music
from the prodigy,

00:00:34.760 --> 00:00:37.170
and it unveils the
real-life chain of command

00:00:37.170 --> 00:00:38.820
if an asteroid was
to hit the Earth.

00:00:38.820 --> 00:00:42.214
It's got its UK premiere on
June 30 at the BFI in London

00:00:42.214 --> 00:00:44.130
and will be available
on all digital platforms

00:00:44.130 --> 00:00:45.701
after that, including
Google Play.

